PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Finance of VIATEUR BERGERON, of Hull, Quebec, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canada Deposit Insurance Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Marcel H. Caron, whose term has expired.
